'''2017年[[全英音乐奖|全英音乐奖]]'''（{{lang-en|2017 Brit Awards}}）是第37届[[英国唱片业协会|英国唱片业协会]]年度流行大奖<ref name=Sun>{{Cite news |url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/1971040/information-on-brit-awards-2017/ |title=NEED TO KNOW When are the Brit Awards 2017, who is presenting and how can I get tickets? |newspaper=The Sun （UK） |publication-date=12 October 2016 |accessdate=2017-02-25 |archive-date=2016-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126003901/https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/1971040/information-on-brit-awards-2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，于2017年2月22日在伦敦{{le|O2体育场|The O2}}举行<ref name=Sun/>。本届首创直播提名揭晓的启动仪式《全英音乐奖来了》于2017年1月14日举行，由{{le|艾玛·威利斯|Emma Willis}}主持。去年11月，[[罗比·威廉姆斯|罗比·威廉姆斯]]在伦敦{{le|托罗斯剧院|Troxy}}获得全英音乐奖偶像奖。随后[[扎哈·哈迪德|扎哈·哈迪德]]设计了颁给得奖者的奖杯<ref>{{cite news|title=Dame Zaha Hadid's Brit Awards statuette design unveiled|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-38160633|publisher=BBC|date=2016-12-01|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2017-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027122453/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-38160633|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年1月13日，[[YouTube|YouTube]]网红{{le|卡斯帕·李|Caspar Lee}}宣布担任典礼网络主持人。原计划担任主持的[[迈克尔·布伯雷|迈克尔·布伯雷]]考虑到儿子正在与肝癌作斗争，“决定关注儿子的康复”，于2017年1月18日推掉主持工作。2017年1月31日，艾玛·威利斯和[[德莫特·欧莱瑞|德莫特·欧莱瑞]]宣布借代布伯雷，主持典礼<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4174252/Dermot-O-Leary-Emma-Willis-host-2017-BRIT-Awards.html|title=Presenting the BRITs is a holy grail!' Dermot O'Leary and Emma Willis to host 2017 Awards after Michael Buble 'pulled out to focus on three-year-old son Noah's liver cancer'|date=2017-01-31|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=2017-02-03|archive-date=2017-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204005718/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4174252/Dermot-O-Leary-Emma-Willis-host-2017-BRIT-Awards.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|爱丽丝·利维|Alice Levine}}、{{le|克莱拉·阿姆佛|Clara Amfo}}和劳拉·杰克逊（{{lang|en|Laura Jackson}}）则负责主持[[ITV2|ITV2]]的红毯和后台节目<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/news/brit-awards-2017-full-list-winners/|title=Brit Awards 2017: full list of winners, from David Bowie to Beyonce|date=2017-02-22|work=Telegraph|accessdate=2017-02-23|archive-date=2017-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222225702/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/news/brit-awards-2017-full-list-winners/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在典礼上，前[[威猛乐队|威猛乐队]]乐手{{le|安德鲁·瑞吉利|Andrew Ridgeley}}、{{le|海伦·德麦克奎|Helen DeMacque}}和{{le|雪莉·霍里曼|Shirlie Holliman}}共同缅怀了已故的[[乔治·麦克尔|乔治·麦克尔]]<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/live/2017/feb/22/brit-awards-2017-katy-perry-skepta-little-mix-ed-sheeran-liveblog|title=The George Michael tribute, the 1975, Ed Sheeran and more – the 2017 Brits awards as they happened|date=2017-02-22|work=Guardian|accessdate=2017-02-23|archive-date=2017-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222230317/https://www.theguardian.com/music/live/2017/feb/22/brit-awards-2017-katy-perry-skepta-little-mix-ed-sheeran-liveblog|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[酷玩乐队|酷玩乐队]]主唱[[克里斯·马丁|克里斯·马丁]]在缅怀环节中献唱<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/events/evfwhn/live/cx3v4f|title=2017 Brit Awards: as they happened|date=2017-02-22|work=BBC News|accessdate=2017-02-23|archive-date=2017-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223160759/http://www.bbc.co.uk/events/evfwhn/live/cx3v4f|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4249686/Andrew-Ridgeley-pays-tearful-tribute-George-Michael.html|title='His legacy will resonate for years to come': Wham's Andrew Ridgeley pays tribute to George Michael at the BRIT Awards following his death as dancers Pepsi and Shirlie break down in tears|date=2017-02-22|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=2017-02-23|archive-date=2017-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223131424/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-4249686/Andrew-Ridgeley-pays-tearful-tribute-George-Michael.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

